---
config:
  theme: neutral
---
flowchart TD
    Start([Start]) --> M[System displays main menu]
    M --> C{User selects option 1}
    C --> I[User inputs id, name, age,<br>salary, work location]
    I --> V1{Code is not null and<br>not duplicated in DB?}
    V1 -- "No" --> E1[Show error:<br>code null / duplicated]
    E1 --> M
    V1 -- "Yes" --> V2{Age in range 18..50?}
    V2 -- "No" --> E2[Show error:<br>age must be 18-50]
    E2 --> M
    V2 -- "Yes" --> V3{Salary > 0?}
    V3 -- "No" --> E3[Show error:<br>salary must be > 0]
    E3 --> M
    V3 -- "Yes" --> A[Add Worker to DB]
    A --> OK[Show success message]
    OK --> M2[Return to main menu]
    M2 --> End([End])
